BJRpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=16da9017\" target=\"_blank\">https://cnews.com.tw/android沒有要消失-google不會與chrome-os整併/</a><br />\nGoogle重申:「Android與Chrome OS並沒有要合併」。<br />\n<br />\n日前，Google業務部門的資深副總裁Hiroshi Lockheimer接受媒體訪問時表示，Android與Chrome OS是兩個不同的執行系統，Android是以手機系統為核心，再陸續拓展到其他裝置，而Chrome OS則像是一台電腦，以桌面、檔案、鍵盤、滑鼠為基礎，再搭配App。<br />\n<br />\n如果將兩者合併成新的系統，對Google來說不見的是好事，所以仍會維持獨立系統。"},{"pid":"e0d55551ae92d4b1a9698b1801826b6e079bf467","tid":129424,"uid":35051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"出到8, 但佢個7.0都未上到， 佢推咁快都無用"},{"pid":"84954c29a7de4f172e1bf34eb3fd19385dacb450","tid":129424,"uid":2955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出版本咁密....<br />\n點都係軟件追唔到硬件發展速度<br />\n有d似pc 發展咁.....</blockquote><br />\niOS咪又係一年跳一個number<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb17c4dad3e69b75ce619f1217dd37ce417a6dce","tid":129424,"uid":34836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f6c6639b888cc0433182fedf4503b91a5d8cbb","tid":129424,"uid":658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"出左咁多代都仲未解決到碎片代問題<br />\n幾先可以做到統一更新<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a27d79c54731158193210d4b3df8200baf2ac8","tid":129424,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左咁多代都仲未解決到碎片代問題<br />\n幾先可以做到統一更新<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo